Creating an flex image from a Virtual Server This script makes a paginated API call to SoftLayer_Virtual_Guest::captureImage().
/* Create an flex image from a Virtual Server The script makes a single call to the SoftLayer_Virtual_Guest::captureImage method to create a flex image. Please see below for more information. Important manual pages: http://sldn.

Operation: GET
URL: SoftLayer_Virtual_Guest/{server_id}
Example CURL:
